Architecture Mies Van Der Rohe - Villa Tugendhat 
Publisher: Muzeum mesta Brna | ISBN: N/A | PDF | 21 pages | 10,5 mb

Few monuments of modern architecture can be as much sure of their fate as the villa in Brno. Its status as a national cultural heritage, now reinforced by its listing among the UNESCO World Cultural and Natural Herltage, will protect the villa against inappropriate occupancy and consequent undesirable alterations.
